Olympics which are scheduled to be staged from 26 July to 11 August.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming portion of the Games will take place between 27 July and 4 August.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lara van Niekerk wrote:\\\"It breaks my heart to be missing out on the Paris Olympic Games as 2024 was the Olympics I have worked for since being a little girl.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lara van Niekerk\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I qualified on two different occasions but due to circumstances beyond my control the times did not count.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic dream is not over, it simply got delayed.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Good luck to everyone competing, I wish I could be there in person but I will be watching and cheering from home.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be back.\\\"\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Lara van Niekerk (@lara_vn_)  Team SA's eight swimmer squad comprises of three men and five women.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2142, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lara van Niekerk\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lara_van_Niekerk\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.041428959799034e-35, \"text\":