ce/Ryk_Neethling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryk_Neethling\"}, {\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ramaala\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hendrik Ramaala\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ramaala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendrick_Ramaala\"}, {\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roland_Schoeman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roland Schoeman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roland_Schoeman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roland_Schoeman\"}, {\"begin\": 2609, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunette_Viljoen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunette Viljoen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunette_Viljoen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunette_Viljoen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos has won a South Africa record four Olympic medals, namely a gold and three silvers.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2681, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.85133231223456e-15, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As reported byThe South African website, athletes who wingoldwill be awardedR400 000, with the coach receivingR100 000.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Silver medalists will earnR200 000andR50 000, while the bronze medal payouts will beR75 000andR25 000for the athlete and coach, respectively.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Men  Pieter Co